ygData.messageBody:
The quality of your connection DOES effect your movement speed. I am flying
as fast as ever with Selo's :) Also lag on your system can cause slow
movement, I move a lot faster now that I upgraded from a P-233mmx to a
PIII-450.

Rokenn
